{"tid":639900,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"原來90年代已經成班大陸仔講 顯示卡 VGA卡","createTime":"2018-04-24T00:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T01:53:31.000Z","uid":51701,"like":73,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"43d475c121dd9c95891e52e62727c34a01cfeecb","tid":639900,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">是咁的, 原來由90年代開始黃金已經係大陸仔集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家成班大陸仔仲想正名<strong>顯示卡</strong><br />\n<br />\n跟我一齊SHOUT：<strong>顯卡<span style=\"font-size: large;\">顯卡顯卡</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">顯卡顯卡</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">顯卡顯卡顯卡</span></div><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>Referrences</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/wgku34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fwgku34.png&h=0dc6e4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FUa40T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFUa40T.jpg&h=2817d898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/computer/20020916/img/f20916_big.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fcomputer%2F20020916%2Fimg%2Ff20916_big.jpg&h=1f01b1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/070542_5b3400db22db51b0a853ea99091476a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F070542_5b3400db22db51b0a853ea99091476a0.png&h=18dc710e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkbookcity.com/image_book/clickpub_88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbookcity.com%2Fimage_book%2Fclickpub_88.jpg&h=bea2d154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050721/Article_LiveMag/21fu1pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050721%2FArticle_LiveMag%2F21fu1pnew.jpg&h=6faa8744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20050721/5067270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050721%2F5067270&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0EEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b37f23cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050721%2F5067270&h=d80ca4ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20050721/5067270</a><br />\n2005年07月21日 顯示卡： Intel Extreme Graphics w/64MB VRAM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><br />\n<ins><ins>Appendix</ins></ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/131407_83687fe830636165be3e697eb4b90bf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F131407_83687fe830636165be3e697eb4b90bf7.jpg&h=7b7e7e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://club-img.kdslife.com/attach/1k0/hb/5w/o52806-1wnu.jpg@1o_1l_600w_90q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclub-img.kdslife.com%2Fattach%2F1k0%2Fhb%2F5w%2Fo52806-1wnu.jpg%401o_1l_600w_90q.jpg&h=720aa5b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a0e8a85be403e20472cde4d9451e94ee8fe4c5d","tid":639900,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma