395ec11e084d8e1e0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F220903_857ba09aadb0e6395ec11e084d8e1e0b.png&h=4d040ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n算啦 冇用嫁啦<br />\n連登同港台蝗化情況一樣<br />\nGOOGLE TRENDS乜都講曬啦<br />\n10年前屌人顯卡蝗語冇人會駁嘴<br />\n依家顯卡已經反超顯示卡<br />\n<br />\n我就唔怪啲唔玩開電腦嘅人講顯卡，佢地都係耳濡目染<br />\n要怪就怪果啲內容農場式運作嘅垃圾繁體網站，直接簡轉繁copy n paste中國評測網站啲文章<br />\n台灣啲網見好多都講緊內存、顯存、CPU主頻嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經冇得救<br />\n香港人就通常都直接用英文RAM VRAM 邊個同你係度內存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"本來我都唔肯定以前係咪真係無人叫顯卡<br />\n但呢張圖真係收撚哂對家皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}